{"tid":748112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那冥幣走勢】中間價穿6.7心理關口    離岸價兌港元見86！","createTime":"2018-07-19T03:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T10:51:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8614e9d6ca7c88b1c67b48758dbfe4ac77449f7b","tid":748112,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180719/large/1531964468_b1f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F1531964468_b1f7.jpg&h=c93b2f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那冥幣繼續尋底，今早離岸支那冥幣CNH在半小時內跌逾160點子，最新報6.7537，在岸支那冥幣CNY報6.7242。每百港元兌人民幣報86.03。<br />\n<br />\n外滙交易中將支那冥幣指導價（中間價）定於6.7065兌1美元，是自去年八月以來新低，亦低於心理關口6.7，同時亦反映官方在美支貿易戰之下，對支那冥幣偏弱幅度仍感到滿意。<br />\n<br />\n支那冥幣於本月已貶值3.5%，是全球31種主要貨幣之中最弱。"},{"pid":"4bd60fd97b79b32f146a0ccd660a29bef5f28ab9","tid":748112,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8614e9d6ca7c88b1c67b48758dbfe4ac77449f7b","tid":748112,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180719/large/1531964468_b1f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F1531964468_b1f7.jpg&h=c93b2f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那冥幣繼續尋底，今早離岸支那冥幣CNH在半小時內跌逾160點子，最新報6.7537，在岸支那冥幣CNY報6.7242。每百港元兌人民幣報86.03。<br />\n<br />\n外滙交易中將支那冥幣指導價（中間價）定於6.7065兌1美元，是自去年八月以來新低，亦低於心理關口6.7，同時亦反映官方在美支貿易戰之下，對支那冥幣偏弱幅度仍感到滿意。<br />\n<br />\n支那冥幣於本月已貶值3.5%，是全球31種主要貨幣之中最弱。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"貶值救國, 樓市股市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8df0a412750451a693ccf4c8c32daed97d486ee","tid":748112,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"25%關稅，咪貶番25%打個和，super"},{"pid":"ae9b9e373be7d6e0a2872dba56d47a2b83972f99","tid":748112,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"SDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa7b552611a69e3a6ec693e1b9863a20ab1a9cd","tid":748112,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"離岸人幣進一步跌至６﹒７８創逾一年低，套利交易增<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社１９日專訊》美國聯儲局主席鮑威爾的樂觀言論，確認美國今年或會進一步加息的預期，並支持美元向上，投資者購匯情緒增加，人民幣匯率則持續向下。<br />\n<br />\n　　離岸人民幣（ＣＮＨ）早段在６﹒７３－６﹒７４水平上落，但之後隨著在岸人民幣（ＣＮＹ）開市後迅速貶值，午後進一跌至６﹒７８，創超過一年新低，大瀉３１６點子，目前在６﹒７７徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n　　在岸人民幣亦不見樂觀，一度跌２７９點子，見６﹒７４２４，創近一年低，目前在６﹒７３水平波動。<br />\n<br />\n　　離岸與在岸人民幣價差近日持續擴大，推動更多套利交易，亦一定程度對在岸人民幣施壓，目前兩者相差逾３５０點子。<br />\n<br />\n　　人民幣兌一美元中間價今報６﹒７０６６，再創去年８月９日以來最低，較上個交易日貶１５２點子，連跌６日。（ｋｌ）"},{"pid":"5a0064b3075a0b5ac78e5ae42162fbfbc73e1389","tid":748112,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滬股連跌5日　受累人民幣貶值加快</span></span><br />\n2018-07-19 HKT 15:15<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1407854_1_L_20180719151842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1407854_1_L_20180719151842.jpg&h=6bfd443b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地股市反覆向下，人民幣貶值速度加快，市場避險意欲上升，股份普遍下跌。<br />\n<br />\n上證綜合指數收市報2772點，跌14點，跌幅0.53%，連續5個交易日下跌。<br />\n<br />\n深證成份指數報9148點，跌46點，跌幅0.51%。<br />\n<br />\n創業板指數報1590點，跌17點，跌幅1.11%。"},{"pid":"c7c57030d437b1f301a9fc3868643850559b9b8e","tid":748112,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"東莞時光快到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff33261ca11ed94e1a66819f7224addcecd52c04","tid":748112,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">在岸人民幣收市跌近590點子　<br />\n離岸價跌穿6.79  創逾1年新低</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1407881_1_L_20180719171732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1407881_1_L_20180719171732.jpg&h=17ac7d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在岸及離岸人民幣匯價都創逾1年低位。在岸人民幣兌美元尾市急跌逾500點子，收市報6.7734兌1美元，較上日跌589點子。離岸人民幣更跌穿6.79關口，低見6.7982兌1美元，一度跌近500點子。<br />\n<br />\n交易員表示，美元繼續受聯儲局主席鮑威爾國會證詞支持，美匯指數企穩在95以上，拖累在岸和離岸人民幣匯價向下，加上離岸和在岸價差擴大，套利交易推動境內匯價下跌。<br />\n<br />\n交易員又指，今日中間價未明顯過濾，在岸價下跌主要反映市場自發行為，但美元兌人民幣3個月以上期限的掉期幾乎全面向下，1年期掉期最低觸及130點，市場估計監管當局正為穩定匯率而儲備力量，因為如果美匯指數其後企穩於95關口，則上行可能性加大，人民幣料繼續受壓。"},{"pid":"2e177f52dda6fc1b6821ac81a56dbbaeee7daad2","tid":748112,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"跌返落1：1先係新聞"},{"pid":"9aab17456b3cddc36910f62b4c21f3d6bf55004b","tid":748112,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e177f52dda6fc1b6821ac81a56dbbaeee7daad2","tid":748112,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"跌返落1：1先係新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c04e659ab4d60cdea632c473b16157adb539315","tid":748112,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e177f52dda6fc1b6821ac81a56dbbaeee7daad2","tid":748112,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"跌返落1：1先係新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"就到90%"},{"pid":"76695b0364753e3b1c20d95c89129ae6b2ccde1a","tid":748112,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"匯率戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6e9df507c0a9e1fb9dd84cd975a6efffa08400","tid":748112,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e177f52dda6fc1b6821ac81a56dbbaeee7daad2","tid":748112,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"跌返落1：1先係新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"2：1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc724c2d8f8d0f7817041df9bedd4783ea81649","tid":748112,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f194dd8fe10aa9316d9a8eed89cca15228021ea","tid":748112,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6e9df507c0a9e1fb9dd84cd975a6efffa08400","tid":748112,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e177f52dda6fc1b6821ac81a56dbbaeee7daad2","tid":748112,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"跌返落1：1先係新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"2：1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"台幣咁4:1啦"}]}